title: New: Unknown – #008
content: Having grown up through the pages of future lovers No Fear of Pop, before spilling over onto Crack in the Road, elusive producer Unknown is now spreading his wings and has debuted a new cut via DummyMag. Still keeping his identity secret, yet hinting at a future physical release, #008 is just the latest in what is growing to be a mightily impressive catalogue of work. Soulful and deeply immersing, there’s a level of intelligence to Unknown’s music that quite rightfully elevates him above many of his peers. Check out #008 below and grab a free download.
